{"tid":1857722,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(醫管局記者會) 睇完得出 三個結論","createTime":"2020-02-02T10:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T14:30:28.000Z","uid":2719,"like":513,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3b86d369725241c85274c668639c4dc5e53e90","tid":1857722,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:05:13.000Z","msg":"1. 呼籲唔好罷工<br />\n<br />\n解決方法﹕<br />\n照罷，就算大爆法後都照罷，忍到最後就贏，依家就係拖你，拖到大爆發你地又會大愛地去醫人<br />\n<br />\n2. 為自己行為負責<br />\n- 真實對白 <br />\n- 暫時未有資料，只係知人數有幾千人<br />\n-  即係預咗有資料會秋後<br />\n<br />\n解決方法﹕<br />\n其他行業工會接力搞罷工，唔好孤立醫護，俾港共集中秋後。<br />\n<br />\n3. 就算你罷工都唔淆<br />\n- 有同事返黎幫手，同埋調配配有人手<br />\n- 有限度提供服度<br />\n- 即係醫護人數攻力未夠仲頂得住<br />\n<br />\n解決方法﹕<br />\n呼籲增加人數戰力，令港共就算叫外人幫手都唔夠人手。"},{"pid":"a8b53ca951cf69204b0a7d0f696bc2551a7ce377","tid":1857722,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f447982dc75fe36fe9c91ad933f85d9be7917d0d","tid":1857722,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5203e0587e2d071faade2e0fe9a0db45eaf1cdf6","tid":1857722,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6012716a58b56607d31e656e38773a2f00da45b8","tid":1857722,"uid":221456,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"明天我罷"},{"pid":"a149e25793cef0445bc7066c8695eec45e1ea9a9","tid":1857722,"uid":26773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"人禍黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e5bc7798b1a9c610